videos.description: Joel Berry II misses the 3-pointer but Cameron Johnson is there to throw down a massive dunk early in the first half against Boston College.
videos.headline: UNC's Johnson soars for strong putback dunk

videos.description: Luke Mayne misses a jumper but the Tar Heels get the rebound and connect with Joel Berry II who knocks in a nice 3-pointer.
videos.headline: UNC's Berry keeps it alive for a triple

videos.description: UNC and Boston College players hit the deck and battle for the ball but Ky Bowman secures it then knocks in a bucket for the Eagles.
videos.headline: Boston College's Bowman finishes after messy sequence

videos.description: Luke Maye hits a couple of 3-pointers at the end of the first half against Boston College that have  North Carolina fans on their feet to applaud him.
videos.headline: UNC fans give Maye standing ovation after back-to-back triples

videos.description: Ky Bowman rises up and throws down the one-handed slam in the second half to shrink the Eagles' deficit against the Tar Heels.
videos.headline: Bowman throws hammer down for Boston College

videos.description: Cameron Johnson finds Luke Maye who knocks in a triple from the left corner for a new career-high of 30 points against Boston College.
videos.headline: Maye hits a 3 for new career high

videos.description: Stanley Manley throws down a two-handed dunk and draws the foul on Luka Kraljevic for the 3-point play in the second half.
videos.headline: UNC's Manley attacks the rim for slam and-1

videos.description: Kenny Williams and Jalek Felton hand the ball back and forth before getting to the rim where Felton throws down the vicious one-handed slam.
videos.headline: UNC's Williams sends Felton to rim for aggressive hammer
